{"tid":2018814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《紐約時報》遭中國驅逐後, 決定轉駐台灣. 台灣政府表示歡迎","createTime":"2020-05-16T00:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T01:43:47.000Z","uid":134071,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"026c4015648f877b21f88ffe8ca546bf9109db4e","tid":2018814,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:09:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1372848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1372848&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=9abc133b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1372848&h=d03201e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1372848</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>遭中國驅逐 紐時等美媒轉駐台灣</strong><br />\n2020-05-15 05:30:00<br />\n<br />\n〔記者呂伊萱／台北報導〕中國三月驅逐美國媒體後，<strong>《紐約時報》發言人昨向本報證實，受中國驅逐令的影響，部分特派記者正搬遷調動至台北與首爾。《紐時》強調，將繼續公平積極地報導中國，也會維持北京與上海分社的運作，希望中國政府允許記者返回駐地。</strong><br />\n<br />\n據悉，今年有七家國際媒體向我國政府申請來台駐點，其中包括三月遭中國驅逐的《紐時》。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《紐時》發言人昨透過電郵回應記者時證實說，「因應驅逐令，部分特派記者將搬遷到台北與首爾駐點，程序還在進行中。《紐時》新聞編輯室對中國的關心絲毫未減，將繼續公平且積極地報導中國。」據了解，《華爾街日報》和《華盛頓郵報》也與我國政府取得聯繫，尚待後續作業。</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院二月宣布中國《新華社》等五家官媒視同政府實體，與中國駐美外交單位受相同限制。作為報復，中國三月驅逐《紐時》、《華爾街日報》和《華盛頓郵報》記者。外交部長吳釗燮當時就在推特公開邀請此三家媒體來台駐點。"},{"pid":"d60038875e1a59ef3503acc5bbf17b14a8d45dff","tid":2018814,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:10:06.000Z","msg":"台灣政府表示歡迎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MOFA_Taiwan/status/1261195146336415744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMOFA_Taiwan%2Fstatus%2F1261195146336415744&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=8cef709f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMOFA_Taiwan%2Fstatus%2F1261195146336415744&h=f63fd1de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MOFA_Taiwan/status/1261195146336415744</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部 Ministry of Foreign Affairs, ROC (Taiwan)<br />\n@MOFA_Taiwan<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s great having @nytimes reporters in #Taiwan. Our vibrant international media landscape is much the richer for their presence. Welcome &amp; enjoy the country&rsquo;s freedom in producing all the news that&rsquo;s fit to print! JW<br />\n<br />\n3:22 PM &middot; May 15, 2020&middot;Twitter for Android"},{"pid":"0a4efbe5694a823dbff4afaa435f42dd736d7667","tid":2018814,"uid":282115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:10:48.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"b94b7d62f998600c34f1dce828db9b2d8e0fc874","tid":2018814,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a4efbe5694a823dbff4afaa435f42dd736d7667","tid":2018814,"uid":282115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:10:48.000Z","msg":"識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d482bc4d7fd2687d2bddae45da0949d11fc58c","tid":2018814,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dcd9e7fafc2564457b0ceea3fb4764f20ca60f","tid":2018814,"uid":156096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a4efbe5694a823dbff4afaa435f42dd736d7667","tid":2018814,"uid":282115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:10:48.000Z","msg":"識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:16:36.000